The paper is about evaluating and comparing deep learning algorithms for image multi-label classification, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of similarity metrics and semantic similarity metrics suggests that the paper may also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of APIs suggests that the paper may also be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
